Package: imgarith
Title: Arithmetic Operations for Images
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Abror", "Maksudov", email = "abrormaksudov@yandex.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides tools for performing arithmetic operations (addition,
    subtraction, multiplication, division) on images, as well as utility
    functions for image resizing and manipulation.
